# This tmux statusbar config was created by tmuxline.vim
# on Thu, 04 Mar 2021

# Commands to generate:
#   1. Start vim in tmux with tmuxline.vim plugin enabled
#   2. Configure tmuxline as desired, if at all
#   3. Run `:TmuxlineSnapshot <snapshot-file>` to generate this file
# Then in tmux.conf, `source <snapshot-file>`
